Key Match Events: Steven Kwan and Andres Gimenez followed up Bo's blast with base hits, and both ended up scoring via a Josh Naylor single and a Will Brennan single.
Brennan then came around to score the go ahead run on a Jhonkensy Noel base hit to right field.
Others: Tanner Bibee threw plenty of strikes on Wednesday afternoon, but the Royals took advantage of that and made a ton of contact against him.
Gimenez made another spectacular catch in the top of the eighth inning and stole a hit from Freddy Fermin.
